claw.wani.language

Class ClawMappingVar

  • java.lang.Object
    • claw.wani.language.ClawMappingVar

  • public class ClawMappingVar
extends java.lang.Object
    ClawMappingVar represents the mapping variable used in a loop-extract transformation.

    In the following mapping option:

    map(v1,v2,v3:i/j)

    The mapping variable i is the "arg" mapping as used as the mapping variable in the function call arguments. The mapping variable j is the "fct" mapping as used as the mapping variable in the function body.

    Author:
    clementval
